                <div class="halfwide halfhigh contentpane"><a href="http://cyclingtips.com.au/2013/06/ten-more-of-the-worlds-coolest-bike-shops/"><img data-original="http://eap-us-eshop.s3.amazonaws.com/eshop/T360/uploads/2015/08/19102526/media_cyclingtips.png"></a></div>
